column5: How about an update on all the highway repair following the storm? Can anyone bring the rest of us up to date on the closings and detours?
[font color=green size=3][b]Not sure which storm or hwy you're referring to but Hwy 105 was back in use within 24 hrs, with a temperary repair. Wish'in I was fish'in on Wabby

When you get to the repair (as of a week ago) pay attention. It was really nothing to worry about, but you don't want to hit it going the speed limit! Pooch
